dct_title_s: Palestine : from the surveys conducted for the committee of the Palestine Exploration Fund and other sources [page 7]
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading, hachures, and spot heights. Shows roads, tracks, Biblical, apocryphal, Talmudic names, tribal areas etc. Princeton copy 2: Mounted on cloth and dissected into 6 sheets. Neatlines trimmed away on some sheets.
